Package: metR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Identification and Visualisation of Differentially Methylated Regions
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Aleksandra", "Brodecka", email = "aleksandrabrodecka@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Przemyslaw", "Biecek", email = "przemyslaw.biecek@gmail.com", role = c("aut","ths"))
    )
Description: Set of statistical tests for identification and visualisation 
  of Differentially Methylated Regions. Along with a battery of statistical 
  tests you will find here functions for ggplotting of identified regions 
  and validation of power and sensitivity of different packages.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
